data.description: Beautiful view of the mountains! Home is located close to the golf course. and near local shopping and restaurants. The yard is fully landscaped and is maintained by the HOA, but you still get the enjoyment of maintaining the small flower beds in the front and back of the house. Beautiful private patio area in back.  Attached 1 car garage for easy access and lots of built in storage. The inside has a very open floor plan. The main floor allows for single level living, with a large master bedroom and bath. Upstairs has a multi purpose area, bathroom and 2 bedrooms.
